- Omitted letters, words or passages inserted interlineally in brilliant crimson ink: e.g., fols. 2rb, 2vb, 5ra, 5va, 6rb, 8va.&#xD;
- Omitted letters or words inserted interlineally in black ink: e.g., fols. 6ra, 9vb, 45va, 80va, 88ra.&#xD;
